# DDD layers — [[project_name]]

## Allowed dependencies

```
presentation → application → domain (interfaces)
infrastructure → domain (model)
apis → domain (DTOs)
core ← all layers (shared types, errors)
```

## Layer rules

| Layer | Path | Contains | Must not contain |
|-------|------|----------|------------------|
| Domain model | `lib/domain/<e>/model/` | Entity, failure, `I*Repository`, VOs | Widgets, BLoC, Dio |
| Domain infra | `lib/domain/<e>/infrastructure/` | DTO, service, mapper, repository impl | Widgets, BLoC |
| Application | `lib/features/<f>/application/` | BLoC, events, states | Widgets |
| Presentation | `lib/features/<f>/presentation/` | Pages, components | Direct infra imports |
| APIs | `lib/apis/` | HTTP, interceptors | UI |
| Core | `lib/core/` | Shared errors, app shell | Feature-specific logic |

## Anti-patterns

- UI or `BuildContext` in `domain/`
- Importing `*_repository.dart` (impl) from presentation — use `i_*_repository.dart`
- Business logic in widgets — keep in BLoC
- Skipping `error_localizer` when adding new `*_failure.dart`

## Enums

Place under `lib/domain/enums/<name>.dart`. Reference from entities and DTOs.
